            "answer_text": "The range of a sensor can be determines from its data sheet. For example an ultrasonic sensor named as HC-SR04 is quite common. You can google \u201cdatasheet HC-SR04\u201d to get the data sheet of this ultrasonic sensor or you can click here https://www.google.co.in/url?sa=t&source=web&rct=j&url=http://www.micropik.com/PDF/HCSR04.pdf&ved=2ahUKEwiszL7bxdDZAhULnZQKHdxQCU4QFjABegQICBAB&usg=AOvVaw3dmnux9AHmdz0U9kpAkw4J Finally the answer to your question is that HC -SR04 sensor range is 4 m. ",
